# !! DO NOT ADD MORE ENTRIES HERE without per-entry preview-deploy verification.
# Two separate outages (3d425f00 + 6ccffc1b) both caused ERR_MODULE_NOT_FOUND
# in Vercel's nft tracer when adding *seemingly safe* directory excludes to
# shrink build surface. Grep'd imports are not sufficient — some transitive
# reference (likely via dynamic import or node_modules path resolution) needs
# one of those dirs present during build.
#
# If build time is the pain, the right approach is to extract more handlers
# to standalone Vercel functions (like api/webhook-pluggy.js) instead.
